{
  "texts": [
    "Additional challenges when employing ChatGPT include the potential for algorithmic bias and limitations in the scope of information retrieval.",
    "Errors and biases may emerge in the results because of AI's reliance on the trained algorithm and available data sources.",
    "Algorithmic bias can also result in biased content generation, such as in anti-Islamic or Islamophobic materials (Malik et al., 2023).",
    "Educational institutions must craft policies to promote diversity and inclusivity when utilizing artificial intelligence tools.",
    "A solid understanding of the functioning of AI tools is essential for policy development and transparency."
  ]
}